Package: kdeconnect
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Adds communication between KDE and your smartphones and similar devices
 Tool to integrate the KDE desktop with your smartphones and similar devices.
 It adds a set of plasmoid, plugins and services to the KDE desktop. At the
 moment it only supports Android based devices.
